            "type": "paragraph",
            "text": "Example:",
            "spans": []
          },
          {
            "type": "preformatted",
            "text": "Everyone is selfish; everyone is doing what he believes will make himself happier. The recognition of that can take most of the sting out of accusations that you're being \"selfish.\" Why should you feel guilty for seeking your own happiness when that's what everyone else is doing, too?",
